title: Gold Adc and Sup searching for a ranked team
body:
Hi, my friend and I are searching for a ranked team. it doesnt matter which division u are. we just want to get the Ward.

Im going to be the ADC (Gold 5) Mains: Lucian, Vayne
My Friend is going to be the Sup (Gold 3) Mains: Nearly every sup

We are also ready to offer our TS 3 for talking as a Team

If u want us to be your Botlane then add "Schwarzer Roggen" and "Bodewig" or contact me on the forum.

PS: We just play 5vs5, we are mostly online in the afternoon till nigth
